Class HttpHeaders.Names

java.lang.Object
io.netty.handler.codec.http.HttpHeaders.Names
Enclosing class:
HttpHeaders
@Deprecated public static final class HttpHeaders.Names extends Object
Deprecated.
Use HttpHeaderNames instead. Standard HTTP header names.
